login.title: We get you one step closer!
login.subTitleOne:
Welcome to VitaNavis™, created by CPP Innovations Labs, one of the world's leading experts on the science of personality. The meaning of VitaNavis is "life ship". VitaNavis™ combines CPP's scientifically validated and reliable personality assessments with the latest behavioral science to recommend actions that you can take to help you navigate a path towards your educational and career goals.

The first step in the voyage is to take our streamlined version of the Strong Interest Inventory®, the SuperStrong™, an assessment used for decades to help users align their personal interests with "life ways", both career and personal. Once you have completed the SuperStrong, you will be sent an email with a link to view your personal SuperStrong insights and begin to explore what careers reflect your interests and may be most rewarding to you.
login.subTitleThree: VitaNavis™ is a product of the CPP Innovation Labs. Since 1956, CPP has been a leader in personality and is known for the science and research behind its gold-standard personality assessments. We look to further CPP's mission of helping people "be better" by utilizing cutting-edge technology and data science to enhance the insight and experiences we offer to people and their organizations.
login.interestAssessmentToFind: interest assessment to find educational and career pathways for you. For each pathway, we link your interests to careers, salaries, job outlooks, skills, and the education you’ll need to meet your goals. In the next 5-10 minutes you can be planning the next steps in your life. Are you ready to start your journey?
